---
const steps = [
  { num: '01', label: 'READ', desc: 'Agent pulls all open bug report tickets' },
  { num: '02', label: 'SPIN UP', desc: 'Agent spins up per ticket with full repo context' },
  { num: '03', label: 'FIX', desc: 'Agent attempts to reproduce & fix the bug' },
  { num: '04', label: 'PR', desc: 'Posts a change request on GitHub' },
  { num: '05', label: 'COMMENT', desc: 'Leaves a comment on the ticket summarizing root cause + fix' },
];
---

<section id="case-study" class="section case-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title case-title">CASE STUDY: JUNIOR</h2>

    <div class="case-intro boxy-box-sm">
      <p>We built an internal tool called <strong>Junior</strong>. It reads our bug backlog, spins up an agent per ticket, and tries to fix each one — fully autonomously.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="pipeline">
      {steps.map((step, i) => (
        <div class="pipeline-step">
          <div class="step-badge">
            <span class="step-badge-num">{step.num}</span>
            <span class="step-badge-label">{step.label}</span>
          </div>
          <div class="step-card boxy-box">
            <p>{step.desc}</p>
          </div>
          {i < steps.length - 1 && <div class="step-arrow">▼</div>}
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>

    <div class="terminal-panel">
      <div class="terminal-header">
        <span class="terminal-dots">
          <span class="dot dot-red"></span>
          <span class="dot dot-yellow"></span>
          <span class="dot dot-green"></span>
        </span>
        <span class="terminal-label">junior_run.log</span>
      </div>
      <div class="terminal-body">
        <p class="term-line"><span class="term-prompt">$</span> junior --run-all --dry-run=false</p>
        <p class="term-line term-output">[INFO] Found 12 open bug tickets</p>
        <p class="term-line term-output">[INFO] Spawning agent for BUG-1042...</p>
        <p class="term-line term-output">[INFO] Agent identified root cause: off-by-one in pagination</p>
        <p class="term-line term-output">[INFO] PR #387 opened → github.com/guardian/app/pull/387</p>
        <p class="term-line term-output">[INFO] Comment posted to BUG-1042 with summary</p>
        <p class="term-line term-output">[INFO] Spawning agent for BUG-1038...</p>
        <p class="term-line term-output">[INFO] ...</p>
        <p class="term-line"><span class="term-prompt">$</span> <span class="term-cursor">_</span></p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="case-callout">
      <div class="callout-icon">💡</div>
      <div class="callout-text">
        <p>The human still reviews every PR and merges. Junior is the <strong>centaur's assistant</strong> — not the other way around.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .case-section {
    background-color: #FFFFFF;
    background-image:
      repeating-linear-gradient(
        90deg,
        transparent,
        transparent 59px,
        rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.06) 59px,
        rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.06) 60px
      );
  }

  .case-title {
    color: #222;
  }

  .case-intro {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto 40px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .case-intro p {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 22px;
    color: #444;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .case-intro strong {
    color: var(--blue);
  }

  /* Pipeline */
  .pipeline {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .pipeline-step {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .step-badge {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .step-badge-num {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--blue);
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  .step-badge-label {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--blue);
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }

  .step-card {
    width: 100%;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .step-card p {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 20px;
    color: #444;
  }

  .step-arrow {
    font-size: 20px;
    color: var(--blue);
    margin: 8px 0;
    opacity: 0.4;
  }

  /* Terminal */
  .terminal-panel {
    background: #1A1A2E;
    border: var(--border-thick);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-boxy);
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .terminal-header {
    background: #2A2A3E;
    padding: 8px 12px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #333;
  }

  .terminal-dots {
    display: flex;
    gap: 6px;
  }

  .dot {
    width: 12px;
    height: 12px;
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .dot-red { background: var(--red); }
  .dot-yellow { background: var(--yellow); }
  .dot-green { background: var(--green); }

  .terminal-label {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: #888;
  }

  .terminal-body {
    padding: 16px;
  }

  .term-line {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--green);
    margin-bottom: 2px;
    text-shadow: 0 0 4px rgba(0, 204, 68, 0.4);
  }

  .term-prompt {
    color: var(--yellow);
    margin-right: 8px;
  }

  .term-output {
    color: #88CC88;
    padding-left: 16px;
  }

  .term-cursor {
    animation: blink 1s step-end infinite;
  }

  @keyframes blink {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
    50% { opacity: 0; }
  }

  /* Callout */
  .case-callout {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    align-items: flex-start;
    background: #E8F5E9;
    border: 3px solid var(--green);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-boxy-sm);
    padding: 16px 20px;
  }

  .callout-icon {
    font-size: 28px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .callout-text p {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 22px;
    color: #333;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .callout-text strong {
    color: var(--green);
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .pipeline {
      max-width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>
